            "text": "GAP\uff1aGeneric Access Profile  Basic requirements of a device  Description of behaviours and methods for device discovery, connection establishment, security, authentication, association   models, service discovery  LE device roles: Peripheral, Central, etc.", 
            "title": "BLE GAP"
